  "methodology": "BEP Research 8-component TCO framework: TCO = GPU + Storage + Networking + Control Plane + Support + Goodput + Setup + Debugging. Goodput uses G_restart formula: {[(t_id + t_chkpt/2) + t_init] × j_size + t_repair × b_radius} × #failures × $/GPU-hr",
